---
layout: base.njk
title: Fun Stuff
description: A little levity — jokes and short stories about Buddhism and practice, from Sit Raleigh.
---

<div class="page-hero">
  <div class="page-hero-inner">
    <p class="page-eyebrow">A little levity</p>
    <h1 class="page-headline">Fun Stuff</h1>
    <p class="page-sub">Practice doesn&rsquo;t have to be so serious all the time. A running collection of jokes and short stories, added to now and then.</p>
    {% include "page-hero-icon.njk" %}
  </div>
</div>

<section class="section section--parchment">
  <div class="section-inner">
    {% if jokes.jokes.length %}
    <div class="joke-list">
      {% for joke in jokes.jokes %}
      <div class="joke-card">
        {% if joke.image %}
        <img src="{{ joke.image }}" alt="{{ joke.text | default('Joke picture', true) }}" class="joke-image">
        {% endif %}
        {% if joke.text %}
        <p class="joke-text">{{ joke.text }}</p>
        {% endif %}
        {% if joke.source %}<p class="joke-source">&mdash; {{ joke.source }}</p>{% endif %}
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <p style="text-align:center;color:var(--umber-lt);">Nothing here yet &mdash; check back soon.</p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
